00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:36.780
a unified coherent system. It was one civilization,
kinda.

00:01:36.780 --> 00:01:42.260
Egypt, Mesopotamia, the states that grew up
in the Levant, and the empires of Anatolia,

00:01:42.260 --> 00:01:44.390
all of them have quite a lot in common.

