00:04:33.599 --> 00:04:37.409
Muslims than any other on earth. So at least
according to that definition, the ancient

00:04:37.409 --> 00:04:42.589
Near East was a civilization. But this is
an episode about the collapse of that civilization,

00:04:42.589 --> 00:04:43.589
so what happened to it?

00:04:43.589 --> 00:04:47.549
Well there we have one of the great historical
mysteries. Let's go to the Thought Bubble.

