00:06:14.379 --> 00:06:19.270
that history is the result of like, humans
doing things. You know, humans are big fans

00:06:19.270 --> 00:06:23.699
of human agency, we like to be in control
of things. Historians have traditionally also

00:06:23.699 --> 00:06:28.249
been just a smidge obsessed with war, so if
we're imagining why a civilization ended,

00:06:28.249 --> 00:06:32.539
we're gonna imagine that it probably involved
